description:
This is a 13 minute workout called 'Feel Better In 8 Minutes | Morning Breathwork Routine' from the channel Breathe With Sandy.
The workout falls under Rest/Breathing exercises and Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Deep Recharge and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This quick yet effective 8 minute breathwork routine is designed to help give you that boost of energy whenever you need a reset. You can do this energy breathwork in the morning, afternoon or even in the evening to help wind down from a long day. Enjoy and share with friends.
